  "page": "Chainmaker",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Chainmaker</b> is a figure of some significance in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, where there is a <a href=\"/index.php/Bronze\" title=\"Bronze\">bronze</a> statue of this figure in the plaza adjacent to the <a href=\"/index.php/Slave_Exchange\" title=\"Slave Exchange\">Slave Exchange</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Barristan_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Barristan-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_events\">Recent events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chainmaker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chainmaker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>While the Meereenese army prepares to engage in battle with the forces of <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Second siege of Meereen\">second siege of Meereen</a>, the remaining <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> in the city, led by <i><a href=\"/index.php/Jaqqa_rhan\" title=\"Jaqqa rhan\">jaqqa rhan</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/Rommo\" title=\"Rommo\">Rommo</a>, gather around the weathered statue of the Chainmaker.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Barristan_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Barristan-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chainmaker&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Barristan-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Barristan_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Barristan_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Barristan I (The Winds of Winter)\">Barristan I (The Winds of Winter)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151527\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 475/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1880/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 471/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n